<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a16Dec1936"><font color="red">16 December 1936</font> <i>NLVP</i> (from Ben Huebsch to Paul L&eacute;on): I learn from Jolas, who is sailing for Europe next week, that he has received a considerable instalment of &ldquo;Work in Progress&rdquo; for publication in &ldquo;transition&rdquo; &hellip;  </div>
